Detailed Description

cvmx_npei_rsl_int_blocks

NPEI_RSL_INT_BLOCKS = NPEI RSL Interrupt Blocks Register

Reading this register will return a vector with a bit set '1' for a corresponding RSL block that presently has an interrupt pending. The Field Description below supplies the name of the register that software should read to find out why that intterupt bit is set.
